<br>
&quot;I seem to remember a time quite a while ago, My Brother, when I picked you up off of the ocean floor after your mighty Trident had been stolen from you. So I would not be so quick to point fingers at me for Incompitence.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He then took a deep breath::<br>
<br>
&quot;I agree they had to have been getting outside help. We will discuss it a futre time Poseidon, when time is more of a luxury.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He then walked over to Hephaestus, and a shadow engulfed them both, and they vanished, moments later, reappearing in Tartarus, right in front of the mouth of the cave, with a heavy door over it, an enormous chain blocking this door::<br>
<br>
&quot;Here it is Hephaestus. Go to work.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=poseidonkofc>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 354<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/4/03 2:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=50>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.theoi.com/image/K2.1Poseidon.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Agreed</span><hr size=1> Poseidon grinned and remembered that moment from some time ago that Hades had brought up. His brother had got him back good. He waved them off as they headed back to try and finish what business was brewing in the Underworld. After they left Poseidon laughed to himself for a while just thinking. When he was done he closed Hephaestus' doors and rode off on his chariot to one of his favorite islands. <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ixhephaestusxi>IX Hephaestus XI</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/4/03 10:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=302.topic&index=51>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Getting to work</span><hr size=1> ::Hephaestus seemed to merely blink and now he was in the bowels of Tartarus. He was used to traveling in a similar method, but not through shadows, through the air the through the smoke::<br>
